  "prompt": "Who makes Clevo laptops?",
  "response": "Clevo laptops are manufactured by **Clevo Co., Ltd.**, a Taiwanese company that is one of the largest Original Design Manufacturers (ODMs) of laptops in the world. Clevo specializes in designing and producing barebone laptops, which are then customized and sold by various brands under their own names. \n\nSome well-known companies that rebrand Clevo laptops include **Sager**, **System76**, **Origin PC**, and **Eurocom**, among others. These companies often add their own hardware configurations, software, and branding to the Clevo base models. Clevo is particularly popular among gamers and professionals due to their high-performance designs and customization options.",
